The sister of Alexander, widow, since 326 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>, of the


<A ID="p87x"></A>king of Epirus. No less than six of Alexander's generals sought her hand in marriage.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
